Fixes: d3c80698c9f5 ("dma-buf: use new iterator in dma_resv_get_fences v3")
Signed-off-by: Ville Syrjälä <ville.syrjala@linux.intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Christian König <christian.koenig@amd.com>
